Tumblebooks Library is an online collection of animated, talking picture books which teach kids the joy of reading in a format they'll love. You may access <strong><a href="http://www.tumblebooks.com/library/auto_login.asp?U=thesslib&amp;P=libra" target="_blank">Tumblebooks</a></strong> from this link or go to our <a href="http://www.thesslibcap.com/e-resources.asp" target="_blank">E-Resources </a>page to read more.</li>
	</ul>
