<h2 align="center"><a href="http://www.cleo.on.ca" title="Cleo" target="_blank">CLEO</a></h2>
<p><a href="http://www.cleo.on.ca" title="CLEO" target="_blank">CLEO (Community Legal Education Ontario/Ãducation juridique communautaire Ontario)</a> is a non-profit public legal education organization that produces clear, reliable, free information to help people understand and exercise their legal rights. They are available in English and French and we have 
